data.description: ntroducing your dream retreat: a spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bath haven nestled on nearly 5 acres of private and secluded land. Step inside and discover a master bedroom that defines luxury, complemented by a generously sized front porch and a sprawling back deck for outdoor enjoyment. Dive into relaxation with your very own above-ground pool, complete with the potential for a pool house retreat.  With plenty of room for your hobbies and storage needs, this property offers an additional storage house and a convenient 2-car garage. Whether you’re seeking tranquility in the heart of nature or an entertainer’s paradise, this home offers endless possibilities. Don’t miss your chance to make this secluded oasis your own.
